  "body": "### Issue\r\nIn [`get_crosslink_chunk_count`](https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/blob/6242e54c0a0cf08f287830f0ddeab217cb2c9d25/specs/core/1_custody-game.md#get_crosslink_chunk_count) function, it uses `attestation.data.latest_crosslink.epoch` to calculate `crosslink_crosslink_length`, but `attestation.data.latest_crosslink.epoch` field is missing after #874.\r\n\r\n",
